<ab>Bischof czu <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir ew vormals
                            <expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>Marckhart<ex>en</ex></expan> Waltman,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, czu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden
                        gesant <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> von <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> lehen
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, als Eberhart Kügelein,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, von <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hochw<ex>irdikeit</ex></expan> czu lehen hat.
                            <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir ew
                            <expan>denselbe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> darynne <expan>gediglich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        bevolhen sein <expan>lasze<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet und im
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gute <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>fürderu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>günstigliche<ex>n</ex></expan> beweiset durch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen, als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in
                        die <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Gregorii anno etc. x<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
